    • getDemographicAdjustment

      PartialDemographicAdjustment getDemographicAdjustment()
      Adjustment of different parameters as a function of age. In general probabilistic parameters will be adjusted as an odds ratio and other real values quantities will be simply scaled by the adjustment value. Adjustments are matched by name.
      See Also:
